Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.31,0:00:15.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢您的惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.29,0:00:19.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.27,0:00:21.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一点都不喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.11,0:00:28.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只拿了一个
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.60,0:00:29.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.09,0:00:33.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还给你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.75,0:00:38.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是来找小都的  不过看来不在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.40,0:00:40.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都？宫崎同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.53,0:00:45.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便说一下我还会再来的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.04,0:02:23.04,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}第10话\N宫崎都的忧郁和初次大赛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.59,0:02:26.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.07,0:02:33.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是老酒铺
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.87,0:02:40.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生意还不错嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.12,0:02:42.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你别傻了！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.65,0:02:46.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛  不是比酒铺的时候更赚吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.59,0:02:48.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知不知道要回交公司多少钱啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.30,0:02:50.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要支出人事费用
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.87,0:02:53.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本没赚多少
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.06,0:03:00.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比以前更拼命  却没怎么赚头
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.84,0:03:02.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊  原来是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.28,0:03:08.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虎侍  你既然回来了就别在家无所事事  快去店里帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.74,0:03:14.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来老妈  我的饭呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.78,0:03:16.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都快饿死了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.83,0:03:17.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.78,0:03:23.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.49,0:03:27.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…喂  这不是店里的商品吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.58,0:03:30.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且马上就要过保质期了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.61,0:03:35.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说了嘛  货款有一半都是爸爸妈妈在出嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.54,0:03:38.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不做咖喱吗？儿子难得回来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.91,0:03:41.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴给我吃！然后去干活！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.51,0:03:44.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸老妈成天都吃这个！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.25,0:03:47.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊  虎侍  你也要帮忙分担家计
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.36,0:03:51.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…我知道了  吃就好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.18,0:03:55.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本来还想吃老妈做的咖喱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.98,0:03:57.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题  这里有的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.05,0:04:01.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了  全是商品而且还快过保质期了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.84,0:04:03.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.62,0:04:06.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,充斥在童年回忆那怀念的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.39,0:04:07.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太幼稚了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.13,0:04:10.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多该变得像个大人了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.34,0:04:16.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虎侍  你晚上来店里帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.72,0:04:19.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.87,0:04:22.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.39,0:04:31.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真辛苦啊  老爸老妈比以前更劳累啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.41,0:04:35.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不能让学校解雇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.23,0:04:37.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能靠家里了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.67,0:04:38.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.84,0:04:42.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么没有香蕉牛奶了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.58,0:04:44.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我平常都有买嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.13,0:04:50.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  那商品现在已经停止生产了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.40,0:04:52.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？没法再进货了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.77,0:04:54.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.94,0:04:59.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  都不考虑到客人的需求  真没用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.96,0:05:02.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  没想法了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.73,0:05:05.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算对我们说这样事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.92,0:05:10.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.49,0:05:14.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大人社会里看到也要当作没看到的没道理的事情太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.40,0:05:16.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发脾气也解决不了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.11,0:05:19.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没道理…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.39,0:05:21.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来帮忙真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.39,0:05:26.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从店铺改成这样后你就没回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.65,0:05:28.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.06,0:05:33.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫石田！请多多指教！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.47,0:05:35.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  真有精神啊  多大了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.90,0:05:38.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十八了  大学一年级
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.40,0:05:40.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为开始自己住所以要开始赚钱了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.73,0:05:42.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗是吗  要加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.07,0:05:46.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近很不太平呢  特别是深夜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.38,0:05:50.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斜对面那家  去年还被抢过了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.64,0:05:51.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.12,0:05:54.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我们有两个人  不过别太放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.81,0:05:56.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我经常偷懒的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.23,0:06:02.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给我吧！我有在练剑道的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.76,0:06:06.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我一把竹剑  来个强盗什么一下就把他搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.73,0:06:10.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可真放心啊  那我去拿一把过来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.67,0:06:16.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  客人来了  把竹剑收好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.90,0:06:17.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.27,0:06:28.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把钱拿出来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.74,0:06:33.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.02,0:06:39.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.73,0:06:42.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要报警…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.47,0:06:44.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.28,0:06:48.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石田君  电话是多少来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.81,0:06:51.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是多少呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.03,0:07:00.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回想起来  我那时开始就逃避  放弃  装看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.15,0:07:03.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不记得有战斗过
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.17,0:07:07.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人生最大的敌人就是没道理
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.95,0:07:11.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与对错无关  只是必须接受的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.09,0:07:16.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大人的社会  是没有任何答案的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.55,0:07:18.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能再输了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.18,0:07:20.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必须站起来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.78,0:07:27.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.14,0:07:29.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与自己的人生！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.34,0:07:40.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,420元
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.01,0:07:41.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.16,0:07:45.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我到时候再回来咯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.68,0:07:49.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.14,0:07:52.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是老爸给你的零用钱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.12,0:07:54.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  不用啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.15,0:07:57.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说了  拿去吧  你不是也帮过忙了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.36,0:08:00.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这倒也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.42,0:08:02.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.83,0:08:06.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好花吧  别去买什么无聊的东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.38,0:08:12.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当我是小孩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.00,0:08:19.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五万…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.26,0:08:25.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是当了一晚的班
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.05,0:08:27.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这太让我窝心了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.72,0:08:32.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是  小田岛礼美？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.15,0:08:36.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我同年还一本正经的叫我小都…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.08,0:08:41.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说呢…她好像在偷东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.77,0:08:42.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是礼美
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.95,0:08:45.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的学校就在这附近的车站旁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.59,0:08:47.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.26,0:08:50.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我们念同所中学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.38,0:08:53.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  上了高中还不放过我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.32,0:08:56.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然归还了商品但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.57,0:08:58.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是通知她家里人比较好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.77,0:08:59.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店长！不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.17,0:09:02.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她家人很难缠的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.51,0:09:04.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我不在这里干的话就完事了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.73,0:09:07.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个死丫头片子…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.31,0:09:09.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但川添同学也只干到今天
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.28,0:09:11.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会很困扰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.90,0:09:15.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你来前台不就没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.94,0:09:17.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.45,0:09:22.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过也是呢  不能总麻烦你们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.28,0:09:25.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,川添同学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.13,0:09:26.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.20,0:09:28.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你的薪水
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.27,0:09:31.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这段时间谢谢你  帮了我很大的忙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.03,0:09:32.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.52,0:09:35.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才是  谢谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.28,0:09:39.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样我就放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.63,0:09:42.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在你已经能招呼客人了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.58,0:09:46.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始我以为你要做到这点还太早呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.31,0:09:50.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然年轻就是好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.25,0:09:52.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还能进一步成长呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.53,0:09:53.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.93,0:09:57.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该说年轻吗？还很小呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.60,0:10:03.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天没有侧座啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.86,0:10:06.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  宫崎同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.63,0:10:07.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.03,0:10:10.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才说的那个人…没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.93,0:10:12.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小田岛礼美？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.77,0:10:15.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系没关系  小珠你不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.16,0:10:19.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来  小珠你是为什么想来打工的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.75,0:10:20.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要钱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.48,0:10:26.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  因为动画的初回特典版DVDBOX就要发行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.55,0:10:33.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…能面不改色的说出这种事情也是小珠风格吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.44,0:10:35.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宫崎同学呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.28,0:10:38.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是为了给段郎买礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.18,0:10:41.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,段郎的生日就快要到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.52,0:10:43.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.53,0:10:46.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就是段郎的生日啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.66,0:10:48.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  糟了  我都忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.06,0:10:51.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  小珠  我先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.61,0:10:55.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是荣花同学的生日啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.71,0:11:04.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.88,0:11:16.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸  祝你生日快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.47,0:11:18.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.21,0:11:36.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放弃Material Puzzle的DVD吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.10,0:11:40.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下没干劲啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.03,0:11:47.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老公你听我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.76,0:11:51.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田边家的义男好像没考上大学啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.33,0:11:54.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经是第二次了吧  真糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.76,0:11:56.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.06,0:11:57.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.25,0:12:00.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礼美  要好好做作业哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.94,0:12:01.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.75,0:12:11.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.65,0:12:17.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.81,0:12:19.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,段郎当主角咯～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.72,0:12:20.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nice Couple…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.75,0:12:46.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一名！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.95,0:12:52.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小次郎老师真早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.67,0:12:53.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好少见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.75,0:12:55.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纪梨乃？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.79,0:12:57.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  已经来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.65,0:12:59.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是部长啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.79,0:13:01.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,许久不经历的大赛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.73,0:13:02.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿出气势来吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.18,0:13:05.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有气势！就不会被解雇！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.17,0:13:10.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是很无聊的动机…不过我还是很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.12,0:13:15.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使无法达成梦想  只要有这个心情就满足了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.35,0:13:18.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么「只要有这个心情」  我可是要被开除的啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.31,0:13:26.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人越来越多了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.87,0:13:28.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,共有十五所学校吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.18,0:13:30.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过女生要少得多
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.40,0:13:33.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有学校一个女生都找不到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.71,0:13:37.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  女子剑道本来人就很少
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.27,0:13:41.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说  「获胜率增加」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.86,0:13:43.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家的珠姬可是第一啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.18,0:13:45.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全国第一啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.24,0:13:47.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不期待团体战吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.61,0:13:50.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次的比赛就当作珠姬全国制霸的前哨战吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.21,0:13:52.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们怎么样都无所谓吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.18,0:13:55.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  说人人到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.31,0:13:58.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.49,0:14:01.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要放到哪里好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.00,0:14:03.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要绕到后面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.49,0:14:11.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有桑原前辈  小都都和荣花
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.83,0:14:13.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明说了8点半集合…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.91,0:14:16.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来打个电话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.89,0:14:26.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思——！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.24,0:14:25.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.01,0:14:31.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡过头了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.40,0:14:32.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.20,0:14:37.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为昨晚突然有文章在我的脑海里忽隐忽现
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.38,0:14:40.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发觉过来的时候就睡了  醒来的时候就已经过8点了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.80,0:14:41.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是睡过了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.87,0:14:44.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  文章没记下来不就没有意义了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.38,0:14:46.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  小都都？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.68,0:14:47.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你人在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.57,0:14:52.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,段郎他迷路了  我正在找他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.22,0:14:56.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,市民体育馆在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.69,0:14:59.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去换衣服先
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.17,0:15:02.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上有个人战  都拿出气势来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.42,0:15:17.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.82,0:15:25.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你们看女生那边
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.44,0:15:28.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里是最高大的那个和最小块的选手在对战啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.23,0:15:29.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.33,0:15:34.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.39,0:15:36.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面有效
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.45,0:15:39.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.57,0:15:40.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,川添？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.04,0:15:45.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,段郎快点换衣服！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.73,0:15:47.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上要轮到段君上场了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.24,0:15:49.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.12,0:15:52.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.70,0:15:54.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.92,0:15:57.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.04,0:16:13.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万岁！万岁！万岁！万岁！…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.49,0:16:15.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得好珠姬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.08,0:16:18.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早知道  能优胜太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.17,0:16:20.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.04,0:16:24.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鞘  你能进到二战也很出色
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.77,0:16:27.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔…不过和小珠比起来…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.82,0:16:30.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在意  拿来比就不对
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.68,0:16:31.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好过分
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.13,0:16:34.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇次  你的对手不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.08,0:16:37.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一回战就遇见全国级选手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.79,0:16:39.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次输了也没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.91,0:16:40.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.97,0:16:42.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过真令人激动啊  全国级的水平
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.37,0:16:45.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  段君呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.25,0:16:48.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那啥表情？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.84,0:16:51.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,段郎可是第二名哦！第二名！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.99,0:16:54.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错！很厉害吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.68,0:16:56.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  是很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.04,0:16:59.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对手不是请假就是比你还外行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.23,0:17:02.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不然就是因为肚子疼而弃权…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.68,0:17:05.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样得来的第二名…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.43,0:17:06.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胜利就是胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.57,0:17:09.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.93,0:17:11.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.89,0:17:14.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下午是团体战  你和纪梨乃接下来…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.48,0:17:16.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.59,0:17:18.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纪梨乃？纪梨乃？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.21,0:17:20.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那边被中学时代的朋友逮住了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.31,0:17:22.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她交际很广的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.40,0:17:26.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在重要的作战会议兼重要的午餐会上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.66,0:17:30.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只有指望她家的可乐饼了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.96,0:17:33.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说  被袭击了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.66,0:17:34.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去找她回来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.38,0:17:38.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中学时候的朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.78,0:17:42.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本不想见以前认识的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.25,0:17:45.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.44,0:17:46.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑色溢出来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.41,0:17:52.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女子个人优胜是纪梨乃你们学校的一年级吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.31,0:17:54.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿  很厉害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.46,0:17:56.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明那么娇小
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.79,0:17:57.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.79,0:17:59.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吃午饭了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.80,0:18:02.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  你们等等做前辈的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.72,0:18:04.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的一年级可就差远了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.41,0:18:07.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们也好好学学人家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.21,0:18:10.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小尾巴翘太高了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.74,0:18:11.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.15,0:18:13.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了对了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.21,0:18:14.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是室江高的新生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.94,0:18:16.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为是东呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.83,0:18:18.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  东？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.45,0:18:21.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天东没有来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.35,0:18:24.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.42,0:18:26.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们部里面没有姓东的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.24,0:18:30.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪了  东她的确念室江高吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.97,0:18:32.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不再练剑道了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.99,0:18:35.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是我们中学最强的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.63,0:18:37.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上高中后放弃了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.43,0:18:38.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.45,0:18:41.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.52,0:18:44.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,段郎～啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.63,0:18:45.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.41,0:18:48.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.39,0:18:49.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.73,0:18:52.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都的也～啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.54,0:18:54.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.33,0:19:14.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是  小田岛礼美？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.42,0:19:15.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我的幻觉吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.75,0:19:17.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么那家伙在这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.33,0:19:20.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说  那家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.85,0:19:22.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算上了高中依然要纠缠我？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.90,0:19:30.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来她真的开始练剑道了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.99,0:19:33.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑道服好合适你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.50,0:19:38.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你变漂亮了  小都
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.94,0:19:42.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午后将进行团体战
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.05,0:19:46.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出战的各位请到馆内来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.63,0:19:49.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！不甘心！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.89,0:19:52.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是再冷静一点就能赢了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.38,0:19:54.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后就能上二回战了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.33,0:20:01.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果团体战获胜的只有小珠吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.74,0:20:06.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方也是四个人所以人数少不是理由
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.66,0:20:08.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女生普遍都少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.96,0:20:10.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.54,0:20:13.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都看起来是不是怪怪的？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.91,0:20:16.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近看起来蛮可疑的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.53,0:20:18.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比赛的时候也无精打采
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.93,0:20:21.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是碰到了中学时候的朋友啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.72,0:20:24.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！她说过不想见到这类人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.91,0:20:30.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样！她遇到了不想碰见知道她过去的人！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.62,0:20:31.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.43,0:20:32.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  没错没错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.45,0:20:36.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答对了  给你加十分…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.91,0:20:38.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…宫崎同学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.63,0:20:41.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不进道场吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.49,0:20:44.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  小珠  我进我进
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.06,0:20:50.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓死我了  她总是毫无声息的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.71,0:20:54.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真惨  最近总是平静不下来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.72,0:20:56.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是笼罩在礼美的阴影下…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.32,0:21:00.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都  我们一起去学校吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.78,0:21:07.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然很奇怪  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.85,0:21:08.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.88,0:21:11.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天大家表现不错！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.67,0:21:14.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  下次的IH大赛预选才是来真的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.03,0:21:17.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标是获胜！进军全国！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.68,0:21:18.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.23,0:21:22.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好加油  我就请你们吃超好的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.44,0:21:24.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上限五万元！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.60,0:21:25.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.46,0:21:26.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五万元？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.48,0:21:28.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的吗？老师
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.38,0:21:30.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是看错了两个零？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.53,0:21:32.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师坏掉了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.48,0:21:33.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.13,0:21:40.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来  小都都状态也不好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.58,0:21:44.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得赶快找到第五个人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.39,0:21:49.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小次郎老师  关于这件事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.10,0:21:54.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好真有哦  第五人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.96,0:21:55.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.35,0:22:02.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…是谁来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.95,0:22:03.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么知道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.14,0:22:22.82,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fs24\fad(300,0)}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.05,0:22:27.84,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}夕闇に  輝き出す  願いたち
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.14,0:22:34.23,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}この手の中 降りてきて 流れ星…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.26,0:22:55.29,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}窓辺で素足のまま  夜を見上げて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.74,0:23:02.32,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}眠れない 月明かり ひとり
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.19,0:23:10.19,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}目の前を ちらついてく 昼間の私
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.80,0:23:17.53,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}自分だけ 空回りで もどかしいまま
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.81,0:23:20.49,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fs24}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.78,0:23:25.53,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}目を閉じて  心の声  聞いてる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.82,0:23:32.37,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}まだ知らない 私に出会いたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.53,0:23:35.37,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fs24}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.62,0:23:40.37,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}まばゆく  輝いてる  願いたち
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.70,0:23:48.05,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}この手の中 降りてきて 流れ星…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.14,0:22:22.82,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(300,0)}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.05,0:22:27.84,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}暮色中闪耀着的那小小心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.14,0:22:34.23,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}寄于手中  希望流星能为我实现…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.26,0:22:55.29,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}在窗边光着脚丫  仰望着夜空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.74,0:23:02.32,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}唯有无法入眠的月光相伴
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.19,0:23:10.19,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}眼前浮现出午时的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.80,0:23:17.53,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}只是徒劳得令人着急
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.81,0:23:20.49,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.78,0:23:25.53,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}闭上眼睛倾听心中的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.82,0:23:32.37,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}依然无法得知  它想与我相见
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.53,0:23:35.37,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.62,0:23:40.37,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}光辉而耀眼的那小小心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.70,0:23:48.05,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}寄于手中  希望流星能为我实现…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.82,0:23:51.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.79,0:23:52.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咱是纪梨乃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.58,0:23:53.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日月轮转快又快
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.18,0:23:58.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咱们竹剑终于也超过十话突入十回战啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.66,0:23:59.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.34,0:23:59.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼓掌鼓掌
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.06,0:24:00.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过奖过奖
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.76,0:24:02.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  现在正在做
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.20,0:24:03.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宣传部长状态正佳！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.66,0:24:05.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…大概吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.64,0:24:06.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在搜寻仍未出现的第五人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.11,0:24:09.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实行捕获成为同伴的充满阴谋的任务中
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.32,0:24:11.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和小鞘会全力以赴的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.16,0:24:11.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一话的标题是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.20,0:24:13.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「动画与梦境」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.88,0:24:16.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是没什么事还是没看下一话的话
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.25,0:24:17.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉出去再教育
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.16,0:24:18.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以节目来讲就是场外！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.51,0:24:19.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合起来就是！一本！
